snippet.title: Michael Imhotep
snippet.description:
Listen to “The African History Network Show”, Monday - Friday 11pm - midnight & Sundays 9pm-11pm EST with host Michael Imhotep founder of The African History Network on 910 AM Superstation WFDF Detroit. Listen to the show at http://www.AfricanHistoryNetwork.com and for Podcasts. Search for "The African History Network Show" where ever you get your podcasts from. 

If you want to advertise your business with The African History Network Show please email us at CustomerService@AfricanHistoryNetwork.com or call us at (313) 462-0003.
